{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> \u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070010/extras/Explore.png?t=1733163658\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The village of Brentwood seems nice and peaceful, but there are many dark secrets hidden that nobody wants to talk about. And it looks like your grandpa\u2019s mysterious death has something to do with it. As you explore, you\u2019ll uncover these secrets and piece together the truth.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070010/extras/secretsGifBasement.gif?t=1733163658\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070010/extras/Solve.png?t=1733163658\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070010/extras/Gif_Puzzle.gif?t=1733163658\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070010/extras/Build.png?t=1733163658\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In Brentwood, you\u2019ll find that even in a peaceful rural place disconnected from social media and the outside world, some villagers are still struggling daily. You\u2019ll have meaningful conversations with residents dealing with grief, self-doubt, and societal expectations. Each interaction will reveal more about their lives and the village\u2019s hidden past.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070010/extras/BuildRelationships.gif?t=1733163658\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070010/extras/Witness.png?t=1733163658\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are multiple endings to the game, and it\u2019s up to you how the story will end. Based on the dialogue options you choose and the more you learn about the villagers, you\u2019ll be able to influence their futures. Will you help them overcome their struggles and achieve their best future, or will you use this information to lead them to their darkest fate?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070010/extras/ChoicesGif.gif?t=1733163658\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070010/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1733163658","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070010/page.bg.jpg?t=1733163658","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070010/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1733163658","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070010/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1733163658","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> \u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070010/extras/Explore.png?t=1733163658\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The village of Brentwood seems nice and peaceful, but there are many dark secrets hidden that nobody wants to talk about. And it looks like your grandpa\u2019s mysterious death has something to do with it. As you explore, you\u2019ll uncover these secrets and piece together the truth.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070010/extras/secretsGifBasement.